step.tex:
\text{Given }\frac{dV}{dt} = 900\text{cm $^3$/s, find }
\left[\frac{dR}{dt}\right]_{R=15}\\
\text{where V = balloon's volume and R = it's radius}

step.reason:
\text{The volume of a sphere is given by }V=\frac{4}{3}\pi R^3.\\
\text{And so, }\frac{dV}{dt} = \frac{4}{3}\pi\cdot 3R^2\cdot\frac{dR}{dt}
= 4\pi R^2\frac{dR}{dt}
